{"tid":468892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以多啲嘢講？","createTime":"2017-11-14T20:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T21:53:57.000Z","uid":11598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a82abd45deaa6b4cdfd814c4babd476ff7c0d055","tid":468892,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩"},{"pid":"63964d5bc9afae9903d97134fa572a36988d4029","tid":468892,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:26:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"105d83d40878a4c4d3ab0a2baf26e27561786b9e","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦"},{"pid":"2b8439097d9f18e10da1cc074cc7e5f31e46e28e","tid":468892,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣撩起個話題"},{"pid":"b94c9adb14b1966b33e1c5dfcaf44391afd36433","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣撩起個話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要搵到一點你係有興趣<br />\n例子打機咪先識打機朋友<br />\n咁唔係個個打機朋友都只係得打機一個興趣<br />\n慢慢去聽其他野"},{"pid":"5d2334e0bd598316f0f38e648be7cc2264e265da","tid":468892,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣撩起個話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要搵到一點你係有興趣<br />\n例子打機咪先識打機朋友<br />\n咁唔係個個打機朋友都只係得打機一個興趣<br />\n慢慢去聽其他野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣識新朋友仔呀"},{"pid":"686ef8c5ed84ca7cba4630f4dffeb958fe374cfd","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣撩起個話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要搵到一點你係有興趣<br />\n例子打機咪先識打機朋友<br />\n咁唔係個個打機朋友都只係得打機一個興趣<br />\n慢慢去聽其他野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣識新朋友仔呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知你係絲定巴 如果係巴就好少少 只要厚面皮去入去個圈子到(當然係本身你係講到兩句) 人地講咩你就跟住去<br />\n<br />\n但係你係絲嘅話就煩好多 你知女人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1342fd06bfa33aeb7bfa50e03b11e424e23edf00","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔dead air真係咁難咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學多知識 之後就識到朋友<br />\n朋友自然會成日講其他野<br />\n你就開始有料去同人吹水架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣撩起個話題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要搵到一點你係有興趣<br />\n例子打機咪先識打機朋友<br />\n咁唔係個個打機朋友都只係得打機一個興趣<br />\n慢慢去聽其他野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣識新朋友仔呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知你係絲定巴 如果係巴就好少少 只要厚面皮去入去個圈子到(當然係本身你係講到兩句) 人地講咩你就跟住去<br />\n<br />\n但係你係絲嘅話就煩好多 你知女人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常好人嘅巴打都唔會亂咁踢走厚面皮入黎圈嘅人 只要正正常就會有交流"},{"pid":"4fca3a5db1ad1f340eb8d84de839c7221d7a08fd","tid":468892,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:37:46.000Z","msg":"好佩服啲人好多嘢講"},{"pid":"fcc4cd0f388fea8d732603a078009b1de78fcfb5","tid":468892,"uid":157411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:38:56.000Z","msg":"點解要勉強自己成為多野講既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babaf90501960de2fffdb319d2d57d40f427809e","tid":468892,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要勉強自己成為多野講既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不想孤獨了"},{"pid":"fcd44281ee960e58f6063ae438d64f1ce8228b8a","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好佩服啲人好多嘢講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我明"},{"pid":"e24ed94e011b6da4ff34251feabd15f1a8cc8678","tid":468892,"uid":62312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要勉強自己成為多野講既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ffd4381e3c36f7c409e57b96755d82456ce74","tid":468892,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:46:07.000Z","msg":"曾經有個人同我講 叫我做自己<br />\n其實我唔記得佢點講<br />\n但諗番 如果要改變自己去迎合人地<br />\n先換到朋友既話 咁果啲朋友係唔係真係你需要既朋友<br />\n同埋唔做自己會好攰<br />\n所以我而家都做緊自己 都好似遇到岩自己既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f81234e45fee0f7e316820e3eee6a754188804","tid":468892,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:49:11.000Z","msg":"唔需要好多野講，有野講就得"},{"pid":"ee9967f764b0a28d4620c48dee85c92002758536","tid":468892,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:18:53.000Z","msg":"平時諗下有無野可以講出嚟  <br />\n留意下身邊 人，生活，事物之類 <br />\n學多啲野 知識  消閒活動 興趣 等等 <br />\n人地開口問你野 你識少少都可以答到兩嘴  唔識就真係好難答嘴 <br />\n所以都係做人細心啲 留意下你身邊發生緊既事 自然會有野講到  <br />\n唔係叫你要奉承其他人 係改變自己"},{"pid":"b2b0e6b267bfeaf26882eee304d3515381166673","tid":468892,"uid":112255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:27:13.000Z","msg":"社交最緊要博學，學習唔同層面既知識，天文地理咩都要接觸，唔需要挖得深，但至少係傾到兩嘴先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f106cd8c07524edf6edd31609a8874845662fa","tid":468892,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:53:57.000Z","msg":"同我傾計練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}